{"tid":1779213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【小心街邊呃錢】屌你真係乞食級人血饅頭","createTime":"2019-12-11T13:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T14:04:50.000Z","uid":73161,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"05de24453a0a5f45f587e0711e3ce9e640626a1b","tid":1779213,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"仆街，啱啱收到個朋友電話，話有手足冇地方瞓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewzrFZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewzrFZP.jpg&h=d38ae22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅相係朋友sd俾我，佢係街邊影條友寫<br />\n咁我朋友就想幫佢問我可唔可以俾地方佢住啦<br />\n我本身都想收，但唔知點fc又有啲危險咁<br />\n而且我個位離佢都相當遠<br />\n條友講到自己<span style=\"color: red;\">又冇電話又冇地方住又冇錢</span><br />\n天氣咁凍，冇理由坐視不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁即刻就用tg搵求宿幫佢搵咗附近嘅先啦<br />\n然後admin話呢啲情況搵教會比較好<br />\n咁我朋友仲幫咗條友<span style=\"color: red;\">打埋俾教會</span>啦<br />\n我屌你老母<br />\n條友就淆喇<br />\n話<span style=\"color: red;\">其實已經搵到工又有地方住</span><br />\n只係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想要幾百蚊應吓急</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友即刻覺得伏，走人<br />\n屌你我本身差啲想幫佢買埋電話同卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家啲乞兒進化到扮魚蛋義士呃錢<br />\n鬼唔望你講嘅大話全部變真<br />\n我屌你老母咩，祝你老母日日俾甴近平中出啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之以後係荃灣附近見到呢條友自己小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7fe4fa672daedc8a5c3ec3c735fa04d7cbcf8b","tid":1779213,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"自推，唔止有呃人物資站，仲有呃人乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e487cf0756bd8ad48bf525f22d38df4f0bd8d0e6","tid":1779213,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim